+class RouterAnchor:
+    """Base-routing anchor: penalise drift of the (mobile) router away from the
+    base model's routing distribution, averaged over MoE layers.
+
+    Mechanistic note -- the anchor is *k-independent*. ``Qwen3_5MoeTopKRouter``
